headline: Cardano Price Analysis: Will Grayscale’s Latest ETF Filing Drive ADA to $1?
summary: Cardano’s 10% weekly timeframe price decline stabilized near $0.82 on Saturday after Grayscale filed registration statements with the SEC for new ADA and Polkado (DOT) exchange-traded funds. The proposed ADA ETF will trade on NYSE Arca under the ticker GADA, tracking CoinDesk’s Cardano Price Index (ADX). Grayscale’s S-1 Cardano ETF ...
